437
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:04,770
Acestea sunt cazurile
de care m-am ocupat inainte.

438
00:30:07,580 --> 00:30:10,730
Ori de cate ori
aveam dificultati,

439
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:15,900
le scoteam si le citeam.

440
00:30:18,540 --> 00:30:20,580
Uitandu-ma la aceste suflete

441
00:30:21,820 --> 00:30:25,060
care se odihneau in pace

442
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:29,460
si gandindu-ma

443
