502
00:34:16,220 --> 00:34:18,330
Nu pot sa inteleg.

503
00:34:18,330 --> 00:34:22,049
Daca a planuit asta
de la inceput,

504
00:34:22,050 --> 00:34:26,840
de ce m-a invatat

505
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:30,670
si m-a protejat
in toti acesti ani?

506
00:34:32,520 --> 00:34:38,470
Am suspectat nenumarate persoane
ca ar fi conducatorul partii razvratite.

507
00:34:38,470 --> 00:34:43,100
I-am suspectat pe aproape toti,
dar nu si pe el.

508
00:34:46,470 --> 00:34:49,140
A continuat sa te ajute

509
00:34:49,140 --> 00:34:52,199
